WEBVTT

00:00:00.300 --> 00:00:03.970
The performance appraisal period begins on October 1st and ends

00:00:04.037 --> 00:00:05.839
on September 30th.

00:00:05.905 --> 00:00:08.475
It's also called the rating period.

00:00:08.541 --> 00:00:10.877
During this time, the Supervisor,

00:00:10.944 --> 00:00:13.847
known as a "Rater" for purposes of the performance appraisal

00:00:13.913 --> 00:00:17.851
process, is responsible for implementing it.

00:00:17.917 --> 00:00:21.287
The Rater establishes and communicates performance plans

00:00:21.354 --> 00:00:23.289
near the beginning of the appraisal period,

00:00:23.356 --> 00:00:27.127
provides feedback to Employees during progress reviews

00:00:27.193 --> 00:00:30.997
throughout the period, conducts an annual performance appraisal

00:00:31.064 --> 00:00:34.501
near the end of the appraisal period (in addition to ongoing

00:00:34.567 --> 00:00:38.438
appraisals throughout the year), and recommends an overall

00:00:38.505 --> 00:00:42.442
performance rating for each Employee at the end of the period.


